theorem interior_closure_eq_univ_of_dense
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hDense : closure (A : Set X) = (Set.univ : Set X)) :
    interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  simpa [hDense] using
    (interior_univ : interior (Set.univ : Set X) = Set.univ)
